text: Ragnarok Online is a 2002 massively multiplayer online role-playing game developed and published by Gravity. The game is based on the manhwa Ragnarok by Lee Myung-jin. == References == Category:2002 video games Category:Free-to- play video games Category:Massively multiplayer online role-playing games Category:Video games based on Norse mythology Category:Video games developed in South Korea Category:Windows games
